      "body": "## Pull request overview\n\nAdds Phase 6 regression coverage and test harness updates for the Task Proposal System, aiming to validate end-to-end proposal generation/submission behavior across Temporal workflow boundaries and the proposals API.\n\n**Changes:**\n- Adds new unit tests covering proposal-stage policy propagation and global/parameter-based disabling behavior.\n- Extends task proposal service + API router tests for promotion overrides, workflow-origin proposals, and invalid-state handling.\n- Updates several Temporal integration tests to align worker topology / runner configuration and adjust mocks for new service constructor requirements.\n\n### Reviewed changes\n\nCopilot reviewed 12 out of 12 changed files in this pull request and generated 10 comments.\n\n<details>\n<summary>Show a summary per file</summary>\n\n| File | Description |\r\n| ---- | ----------- |\r\n| tests/unit/workflows/temporal/workflows/test_run_proposals.py | New unit coverage for the workflow proposal stage behavior and policy propagation. |\r\n| tests/unit/workflows/task_proposals/test_service.py | Adds a unit test for runtime override behavior during proposal promotion. |\r\n| tests/unit/workflows/adapters/test_secret_redaction.py | Adds unit tests for `DatabaseSecretResolver` behavior and invalid UUID handling. |\r\n| tests/unit/api/routers/test_task_proposals.py | Adds API tests for workflow-origin creation and invalid-state promotion rejection. |\r\n| tests/integration/workflows/temporal/workflows/test_run.py | Adjusts integration test setup for proposals stage enablement and activity queue routing. |\r\n| tests/integration/temporal/test_oauth_session.py | Uses `UnsandboxedWorkflowRunner` for OAuth session workflow worker. |\r\n| tests/integration/temporal/test_managed_runtime_live_logs.py | Updates unpacking to match `stream_and_parse` return signature. |\r\n| tests/integration/temporal/test_integrations_monitoring.py | Passes mocked `client_adapter` into `TemporalExecutionService` during integration tests. |\r\n| tests/integration/services/temporal/workflows/test_agent_run.py | Updates expected provider-profile manager workflow ID prefix in mocks. |\r\n| tests/conftest.py | Sets global test default `enable_task_proposals = False`. |\r\n| mock_temporal_adapter.patch | Adds a patch artifact file (appears unintended). |\r\n| docs/tmp/015-TaskProposalSystemPlan.md | Marks Phase 6 status as DONE. |\n</details>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n---\n\n\ud83d\udca1 <a href=\"/MoonLadderStudios/MoonMind/new/main?filename=.github/instructions/*.instructions.md\" class=\"Link--inTextBlock\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Add Copilot custom instructions</a> for smarter, more guided reviews. <a href=\"https://docs.github.com/en/copilot/customizing-copilot/adding-repository-custom-instructions-for-github-copilot\" class=\"Link--inTextBlock\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Learn how to get started</a>.",
